Paper: hep-th/0002247

Date: 2000-02-29

Title: A uniform model of the massive spinning particle in any dimension

Authors: S. L. Lyakhovich, A. A. Sharapov, K. M. Shekhter

Comments: Latex, revised version of hep-th/9811003

Journal-ref: Int.J.Mod.Phys. A15 (2000) 4287-4300

The general model of an arbitrary spin massive particle in any dimensionalspace-time is derived on the basis of Kirillov - Kostant - Souriau approach. Itis shown that the model allows consistent coupling to an arbitrary backgroundof electromagnetic and gravitational fields.